{
  "stem": "9995.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this shooting all around, and we had to step even over some dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was incredible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I said that during the first deportation, there was blood flowing on the street, that they have to hose this down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This time, it was much-- I mean, the whole world was-- was red.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's-- the picture was absolutely incredible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was actually the first time that I said to myself, I don't think we will survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because it's going to be more and more of this thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were hoping that maybe the war will end soon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was one of the lucky few.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I was coming out every day to clean the ghetto from concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then somehow, we were able to see some of our Catholic gentile friends who were bringing us some food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we put a lot of money, a lot of jewelry, to my husband's former worker, who was also took over when his father died before the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was coming also in the beginning and bringing us some food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so it wasn't-- And my mother was working for this guy [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mudrich ?], who every day was giving every worker around bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she was bringing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we-- as we're coming also to the barracks, we could have the bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother was bringing this for my husband's cousins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was able to bring some other kind of food, some butter, and even some fruit and vegetable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, once they caught us, and they were about to kill us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I ate half a pound of butter, because if they found it, I knew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were beating you up to a bloody pulp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
